{"word":"ἰατρεύω","slug":"ἰατρεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰατρεύω</b></el> <el>(ἰᾱτρεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἰατρός'><el>ἰατρός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to treat medically, to cure</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be under medical care</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to practise medicine</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}